            "author": 1015,
            "body": "<p><img src=\"/uploads/ueditor/20181029/1540822488726324.png\" title=\"1540822488726324.png\" alt=\"IMG_20181029_203003.png\"></p><p>勇敢的心</p><p>Freedom!</p><p><br></p><p><img src=\"/uploads/ueditor/20181029/1540822538858130.png\" title=\"1540822538858130.png\" alt=\"IMG_20181029_203054.png\"></p><p>野马<br></p><p>脱离保守与家庭束缚</p><p><br></p><p><br></p><p><img src=\"/uploads/ueditor/20181029/1540822662687771.png\" title=\"1540822662687771.png\" alt=\"IMG_20181029_203528.png\"></p><p>辩护人</p><p>这个我不知道算不算，它是根据真实事件改编的，一个独立的律师变成了维权人士。</p><p><br></p><p><img src=\"/uploads/ueditor/20181029/1540822760625089.png\" title=\"1540822760625089.png\" alt=\"IMG_20181029_203614.png\"></p><p>金色梦乡</p><p>跑吧，我们无力对抗，但也不能让他们得逞。<br></p><p><br></p><p><img src=\"/uploads/ueditor/20181029/1540822897769630.png\" title=\"1540822897769630.png\" alt=\"IMG_20181029_221300.png\"></p><p>美女与猎犬<br></p><p>讲的是突尼斯茉莉花革命的前一夜，茉莉花开，黎明到来。</p><p><br></p><p><img src=\"/uploads/ueditor/20181029/1540822986629369.png\" title=\"1540822986629369.png\" alt=\"IMG_20181029_221310.png\"></p><p>奇异的恩典<br></p><p>讲述的是理想主义者威廉威伯福斯长期在英国国会长期进行反黑奴运动。<br></p><p><br></p><p><img src=\"/uploads/ueditor/20181029/1540823170409079.png\" title=\"1540823170409079.png\" alt=\"IMG_20181029_221322.png\"></p><p>第四公民</p><p>讲述的是斯诺登与美国政府斗争的故事，曝光了令全球震惊的棱镜门事件。</p><p><br></p><p><img src=\"/uploads/ueditor/20181029/1540823239260158.png\" title=\"1540823239260158.png\" alt=\"IMG_20181029_221336.png\"></p><p>1987黎明到来的那一刻</p><p><br></p>",
